Definition: Axuni is a cool, calm person who sees the best in people even when others don't. Axuni is hard headed and funny with friends and family. Axuni knows how to make people laugh but once on his bad side there is no going back because he will come at you with every single kind of torturing words you can think of. He is an exemplary friend and student as well as a great athlete. He is also very popular cool and known by everyone.
